@using QuanLyMamNon.Models
@model QuanLyMamNon.Models.Dao.ViewModelDanhSachHS
@using (Html.BeginForm("Update", "HocSinh", FormMethod.Post, new { @role = "form", @data_toggle = "validator" }))
{
    @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
    <div class="modal-header modal-header-primary">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
        <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Sửa thông tin</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
        @Html.HiddenFor(x => x.hocsinh.MaHocSinh)
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="panel panel-primary">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        Thông tin học sinh
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <label>Họ và tên</label>(<i class="fa fa-star" style="color:red"></i>)
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-child"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.Ten, new { @class = "form-control", @data_error = "Please enter name field.", @placeholder = "Nhập tên...", @required = "required" })
                        </div>
                        <label>Ngày sinh</label>(<i class="fa fa-star" style="color:red"></i>)
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-calendar"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.NgaySinh, "{0:yyyy-MM-dd}", new { @type = "date", @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Ngày sinh...", @required = "required" })
                        </div>
                        <label>Giới tính</label>(<i class="fa fa-star" style="color:red"></i>)
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-leaf"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.DropDownListFor(x => x.hocsinh.GioiTinh, new SelectList(new List<string> { "Nam", "Nữ" }, Model.hocsinh.GioiTinh.ToString()), "--Chọn giới tính--", new { @class = "form-control", @required = "required" })
                        </div>
                        <label>Địa chỉ</label>(<i class="fa fa-star" style="color:red"></i>)
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-home"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.DiaChi, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Địa chỉ...", @required = "required" })
                        </div>
                        <label>Chiều cao, cân nặng</label>
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-arrows-v"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.ChieuCao, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Chiều cao..." })
                            <span class="input-group-addon">.cm</span>
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-arrows-h"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.CanNang, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Cân nặng..." })
                            <span class="input-group-addon">.kg</span>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="panel panel-primary">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        Thông tin phụ huynh
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <label>Họ và tên</label>(<i class="fa fa-star" style="color:red"></i>)
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-user"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.TenPhuHuynh, new { @class = "form-control", @data_error = "Please enter name field.", @placeholder = "Nhập tên...", @required = "required" })
                        </div>
                        <label>Ngày sinh</label>(<i class="fa fa-star" style="color:red"></i>)
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-calendar"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.NgaySinhPhuHuynh, "{0:yyyy-MM-dd}", new { @type = "date", @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Ngày sinh...", @required = "required" })
                        </div>
                        <label>Số chứng minh thư</label>
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.SoCmt, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Số chứng minh thư..." })
                        </div>
                        <label>Số điện thoại</label>(<i class="fa fa-star" style="color:red"></i>)
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-phone"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.Sdt, new { @class = "form-control", @type = "tel", @pattern = "([0-9+ _-]{9,15})", @required = "required", @placeholder = "Số điện thoại... (ký tự số từ 0-9, độ dài 9-15 ký tự(ví dụ '01676983088')" })
                        </div>
                        <label>Email</label>(<i class="fa fa-star" style="color:red"></i>)
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.Email, new { @class = "form-control", @type = "email", @data_error = "Bruh, that email address is invalid", @required = "required", @placeholder = "john@doe.com" })
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div><div class="panel panel-primary">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <label>Tình trạng hoạt động </label>
                            @Html.CheckBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.TrangThai, new { @class = "form-control checkTrangThai" })

                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <label>Là đối tượn con MTA</label>
                            @Html.CheckBoxFor(x => x.hocsinh.DoiTuongMTA, new { @class = "form-control" })
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 showHide">
                        <div class="form-group input-group DropListLop">
                            <label>Chọn lớp học</label>
                            @Html.DropDownListFor(x=>x.hocsinh.MaLop,new SelectList(Model.listLop, "MaLop", "TenLop",Model.hocsinh.MaLop), "None", new { @class = "form-control dropdownLop", @required = "required" })
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <label>Tình trạng học tập</label>
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-comments"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextAreaFor(x => x.hocsinh.TinhTrang, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Tình trạng học tập..." })
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <label>Ghi chú</label>
                        <div class="form-group input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                <i class="fa fa-comments"></i>
                            </span>
                            @Html.TextAreaFor(x => x.hocsinh.GhiChu, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Ghi chú..." })
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Đóng</button>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Chỉnh sửa</button>
    </div>
}
